features: Airline-Approved Boarding Size: 20 inch carry on luggage meets most airline requirements for overhead compartments. Suitcases with wheels are suitable for 3-5 day trips, air, train and bus travel. Travel luggage is upgraded with double-ended zippers and side-mounted TSA-approved locks to ensure smooth and hassle-free airline baggage screening for carry on suitcase measuring 22x14x9 inches with spinner wheels and handle. It has a volume of 35 liters and weighs only 6.83 lbs.

20% Upgraded Bigger Expandable Design: The checked luggage is ingeniously designed with two main compartments and features the buckle compression system, keeping your clothes neatly arranged. The travel suitcase comes with a zippered mesh pocket for quick access to essentials, and a built-in small pocket for small items. Pulling open the zipper can expand by 1.6 inches, adding an extra 7L of space, with a large capacity of 42L, helping you pack more items and keep your travel items organized.

Excellent Craftsmanship: This hard shell carry on luggage is made of 100%PC for exceptional strength, flexibility, and lightness. The underseat carry on luggage with wheels has passed the shock drop test. The hard shell luggage texture is extremely scratch-resistant and not easily scratched, keeping the hard case luggage looking great on trip after trip.

Superior Maneuverability: The rolling suitcase buttery smooth 360° swivel wheels are extremely quiet and durable, making it easy to navigate through airports, train platforms, sidewalks, and even cobblestone streets. The travel luggage has been upgraded with a sturdy and smooth four-level adjustable aluminum handle with multiple height options for your comfort. Soft silicone handles on the top and sides of the hard shell suitcases have been added to make the lightweight suitcase easier to lift.

Premium Service And Warranty: BAGSMART will back each piece of tsa approved carry on luggage with a 2-year manufacturer's warranty. Before shipment, hard sided luggage with spinner wheels undergoes thousands of rigorous tests to ensure that our luggage meets strict standards and can withstand any journey. If there is any quality problem, please feel free to contact us. Professional and patient customer service will reply to your satisfaction in time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice basic suitcase 4.5 stars
reviews.reviewText: I thought this bag was nice overall. Lightweight, the telescoping handle works well and expands smoothly. The wheels move nicely and smoothly as well. The zipper opener and closed without issue. When the bag was fully weighed down it struggled a little but nothing major. For $100 it's not bad but for this price I wish they made it expandable!

reviews.reviewText: Very small but perfect for short getaways. Hard shell is durable. Rolls and maneuvers easily. Price point is a little high in my opinion but still satisfied

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Superb Hard Shell Carry-On Bag
reviews.reviewText: The BAGSMART airline approved carry-on bag is excellent in just about every way. It is a great looking bag and well designed, with really nice features. The bag has a built-in telescoping handle that locks at various heights to accommodate anyone no matter how tall. The spinners are super smooth and the perfect size, they roll without almost any resistance at all. It also has a TSA lock that can be opened either by a TSA key or combination code. Inside, the bag has everything you need to keep the contents secure and packed tight. Straps, zippered pockets, zippered compartment dividers, etc., and it is also expandable by almost two inches as well. There are built-in soft handles on the top as well as the side to provide convenient pick up and carry options too. This is the best hard-shell carry-on that I have owned and recommend it. Awesome bag!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This little suitcase serves its purpose. I love that it has the lock on it so no one can just open your bag. It also has an extra zipper to make the suitcase bigger if you’re having a hard time closing. The black is perfect and not easy to dirty. Great suitcase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It seems to be the ok. My issue is the handle. It seems to collapse when it wants to after it’s been fully extended.Otherwise, it’s a good item.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty Good Suitcase
reviews.reviewText: Good for the price. I really like how it has the TSA certified lock on the side. The hard side feels slightly thin on the front and back, so I have a feeling it will get dented up at the airport. The wheels are quite average too. They are pretty smooth when moving, but they get caught slightly when changing direction. Still, for the price I can recommend this suitcase.
